{"translation-revision-date":"2025-02-04T15:33:29+00:00","generator":"WP-CLI\/2.12.0","source":"admin-core\/assets\/build\/onboarding-app.js","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","lang":"en","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1);"},"Spectra":["Widma"],"Elementor":["Elementor"],"Bricks":["Ceg\u0142y"],"Other":["Inne"],"Email address":["Adres e-mail"],"Reset":["Resetuj"],"Processing":["Przetwarzanie"],"Access all of our pro templates when you upgrade your plan to CartFlows Pro today.":["Uzyskaj dost\u0119p do wszystkich naszych profesjonalnych szablon\u00f3w, gdy dzi\u015b zaktualizujesz sw\u00f3j plan do CartFlows Pro."],"Get CartFlows Pro":["Pobierz CartFlows Pro"],"Back":["Wstecz"],"Importing..":["Importowanie.."],"Active":["Aktywny"],"Let's Start":["Zacznijmy"],"Welcome to CartFlows":["Witamy w CartFlows"],"You're only minutes away from having a more profitable WooCommerce store! This short setup wizard will help you get started with CartFlows.":["Jeste\u015b tylko kilka minut od posiadania bardziej dochodowego sklepu WooCommerce! Ten kr\u00f3tki kreator konfiguracji pomo\u017ce Ci rozpocz\u0105\u0107 prac\u0119 z CartFlows."],"Save & Continue":["Zapisz i kontynuuj"],"Saving":["Zapisywanie"],"Hi there! Tell us which page builder you use.":["Cze\u015b\u0107! Powiedz nam, kt\u00f3rego kreatora stron u\u017cywasz."],"Install & Activate":["Zainstaluj i aktywuj"],"Installing Required Plugins":["Instalowanie wymaganych wtyczek"],"Since CartFlows uses WooCommerce, we'll set it up for you along with Cart Abandonment and Stripe Payments so you can recover abandoned orders and easily accept payments.":["Poniewa\u017c CartFlows korzysta z WooCommerce, skonfigurujemy go dla Ciebie wraz z Porzuceniem Koszyka i P\u0142atno\u015bciami Stripe, aby\u015b m\u00f3g\u0142 odzyskiwa\u0107 porzucone zam\u00f3wienia i \u0142atwo akceptowa\u0107 p\u0142atno\u015bci."],"Continuing\u2026":["Kontynuuj\u0105c\u2026"],"Continue":["Kontynuuj"],"First Name":["Imi\u0119"],"Please enter your name":["Prosz\u0119 wprowadzi\u0107 swoje imi\u0119"],"Enter Your Email":["Wprowad\u017a sw\u00f3j e-mail"],"Please Enter Name":["Prosz\u0119 wprowadzi\u0107 imi\u0119"],"Entered email address is not a valid email":["Wprowadzony adres e-mail nie jest prawid\u0142owym adresem e-mail"],"Please Enter Email ID":["Prosz\u0119 wprowadzi\u0107 identyfikator e-mail"],"Skip":["Pomi\u0144"],"Select Color":["Wybierz kolor"],"Recommended":["Zalecane"],"Upload a Logo":["Prze\u015blij logo"],"Change a Logo":["Zmie\u0144 logo"],"Remove logo":["Usu\u0144 logo"],"Suggested Dimensions: 180x60 pixels":["Sugerowane wymiary: 180x60 pikseli"],"Oops!!! No templates found":["Ups!!! Nie znaleziono szablon\u00f3w"],"Seems like no templates are available for chosen page editor. Don't worry, you can always import the store checkout template from the CartFlows setting menu.":["Wygl\u0105da na to, \u017ce nie ma dost\u0119pnych szablon\u00f3w dla wybranego edytora stron. Nie martw si\u0119, zawsze mo\u017cesz zaimportowa\u0107 szablon kasy sklepu z menu ustawie\u0144 CartFlows."],"Skip to Next":["Przejd\u017a do nast\u0119pnego"],"Now let's setup your new store checkout.":["Teraz skonfigurujmy kas\u0119 w Twoim nowym sklepie."],"Choose one of the store checkout designs below. After setup you can change the text and color or even choose an entirely new store checkout design.":["Wybierz jeden z poni\u017cszych projekt\u00f3w kasy sklepowej. Po skonfigurowaniu mo\u017cesz zmieni\u0107 tekst i kolor lub nawet wybra\u0107 zupe\u0142nie nowy projekt kasy sklepowej."],"Import & Continue":["Importuj i kontynuuj"],"Processing..":["Przetwarzanie.."],"Importing Failed..":["Importowanie nie powiod\u0142o si\u0119.."],"Change Primary Color":["Zmie\u0144 kolor podstawowy"],"Learn more about usage tracking":["Dowiedz si\u0119 wi\u0119cej o \u015bledzeniu u\u017cytkowania"],"Documentation":[""],"Something went wrong":[""],"An unexpected error occurred while loading this secti